name: Corneo's Nipple Rings Embedding
description:
This is a Textual Inversion embedding to add nipple rings to nipples! It's a very tricky one to get right, it's not as good/consistent as my other released embeddings, but I've had a number of non-character-embed failures in a row now so I wanted to put one of them out there!

It is quite wonky and won't look correct on probably even the majority of generations using it so fair warning. It's specifically trained on nipple rings so won't work for general piercings, though you could try mixing it with normal nipple_piercing tags. It should work for most characters though, doesn't just have to be female breasts, and it might benefit from a higher step count than normal. Inpainting can also give mixed results, but if you get an image or composition you like you can inpaint the nipples with this until you're happy (that said, all examples are txt2img).

Example images produced with my 7th Heaven mix available here https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
